Is it going to shoot again?
That is not good...

rows.label: bf09040100_0040
rows.name:
Superbia's Divine Beast is said
to be at the end of its lifespan.

rows.label: bf09040100_0050
rows.name:
If it discharges any more
ether energy from within its body...

rows.label: bf09040100_0070
rows.name:
Its joints would fail under its own weight
and it would collapse...
